<p>
<lb n="1"/>purakarakairavāptaśaśibhūriśa kābdamu lōppa śā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṁrjñikini sarasipuraṁbulō nili pe saṁddhīyadīpa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mu venni seṭṭikiṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> dāruṇi ya ghaṁṭṭasālapuri dārama
<lb n="4" break="no"/>kunu phala moṁdda vīrikini varasutayaina vāsama
<lb n="5"/>druvaṁbuga nāśaśitārakaṁbugānu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> yī saṁdyadī
<lb n="6" break="no"/>pamu sēkoni(koni) kannamapaṁṇḍitulu nāmanayu reṁ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṇḍu saṁdhyala naḍapaṁggalavāru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
